Lokhu kungenxa yokuthi laba abangayilokothi inyama abayizwa eyokulokhu kubulawa izilwane, zidliwa ngabathandi benyama. Bathi bonke abantu abazitike ngemifino nokunye kodwa bahlukane nenyama. Ukusatshiswa kwabo sekuholele ekutheni iningi losomabhizinisi abahweba ngenyama baqinise ezokuphepha ngenxa yokwanda kwezigameko zokulinyazwa kwezitolo zabo. Ezinye zezilaha azigcini ngokulinyazwa kodwa ziphinde zibhalwe ngegazi lokwenziwa, esabisa abanikazi bezilaha ukuba bayeke ukubulala izilwane. USihlalo wenhlangano yosomabhizinisi abadayisa inyama, uMnuz Jean-Francois Guihard, udalule ukuthi amabhusha asedolobheni iHauts-de-France nase-Iccitanie yiwona ahlaselwa kakhulu. “Sesithembe ukuthi uhulumeni usivikele kulaba bantu abalokhu besihlasela thina namabhizinisi ethu njengoba belokhu beqhubekile nalezi zenzo zabo,” kusho uGuihard. Phezu kokuba inyama ithandwa kakhulu kuleli lizwe kodwa sibukeka sehla isibalo sabayidlayo eFrance. Lokhu sekube nomthelela wokuthi amabhusha athwale kanzima ngoba ayisathengwa kakhulu uma kuqhathaniswa neminyaka edlule. - The Daily Mail